<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.1 (STRIPS 1-2) MACHENGYUAN 9: 195-196 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.1">古公見大公望於呂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.2">遂曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.3">“吾聞周宗有難，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.4">而不[...] 【1】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.5">[...] 榗（?)，[...] ?,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.6">聞光烈之族.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-1a.7">古公 [...]【2】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.2 (STRIP 3) MACHENGYUAN 9: 197 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 有慶，[...] ??,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.2">子嘗以此謑之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.3">其白黑將可知也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-2a.4">古公【3】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.3 (STRIPS 4-5) MACHENGYUAN 9: 199-200 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.1">子訪之尚父舉治.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.2">文王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.3">“日短而世困(?)【4】 ????</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.4">[...] 得尚父，[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.5">載我天下.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.6">子失尚父，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.7">遂我周懼.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-3a.8">既言而尚父乃階至.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.4 (STRIPS 5-6) MACHENGYUAN 9: 200-201 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.1">惟七年，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.2">文【5】王訪於尚父，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.3">曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.4">“我左患右難，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.5">吾欲達中持道.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.6">昔我得中，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-4a.7">世世毋有後悔.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.5 (STRIPS 6-7) MACHENGYUAN 9: 201-202 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.1">惟【6】道有所修，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.2">非天之所向，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.3">莫之能得，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.4">當退而思之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-5a.5">其唯賢民乎?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.6 (STRIPS 7-8) MACHENGYUAN 9: 202-204 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.1">子爲我【7】之道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.2">寡人不能一焉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.3">而介𦁉代之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.4">夫立民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.5">天下之難事也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.6">或以興，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.7">或以亡，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-6a.8">公其盡之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.7 (STRIPS 8-10) MACHENGYUAN 9: 204-206 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.1">夫【8】顧監于下，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.2">乃語周之先祖曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.3">天之所向，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.4">若或與之；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.5">天之所背，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.6">若拒之；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.7">物有所總[==從]【9】也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-7a.8">非天子之差[=佐]也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.8 (STRIPS 10-12) MACHENGYUAN 9: 206-207 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.1">請私之於夫子.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.2">昔者，舜以大 [...]【10】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.3">[...] 乃往.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.4">既見，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.5">將反，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.6">文王乃 [...]【11】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-8a.7">[...]安恭以 [...]【12】???</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.9 (STRIP 13) MACHENGYUAN 9: 208 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.1">[...] 五殺不舉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.2">其民能相分餘；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.3">三年不生粟，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.4">五年亡凍餒者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-9a.5">此[...]之善也.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.10 (STRIPS 13-15) MACHENGYUAN 9: 208-211 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.1">文王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.2">“請【13】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.3">[...]見[人疐（陟?）]，湯 （修?理?）善見設（?)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.4">文王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.5">“道有要乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.6">尚父曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.7">“敬人而親道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.8">毋自設而信 [...]【14】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-10a.9">於是用將焉.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.11 (STRIPS 15-17) MACHENGYUAN 9: 211-212 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.1">文王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.2">“請問其 [...] 矣. 【15】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.3">尚父乃言曰：[...].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.4">“夫先四帝，"</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.5">二王之[...]【16】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.6">[...]啓行五度，[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-11a.7">湯行三起.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.12 (STRIP 17) MACHENGYUAN 9: 212 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.1">文王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.2">“道有守乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.3">尚父曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.4">“黃帝俫[=釐]光，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-12a.5">堯 [...]【17】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.13 (STRIPS 18-19) MACHENGYUAN 9: 213-214 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.1">[...] 茖.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.2">尚父曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.3">“黃帝修三員 [...] 【18】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-13a.4">[...]不知其所極.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.14 (STRIPS 19-20) MACHENGYUAN 9: 214-215 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.1">文王曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.2">“有後蓋乎?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.3">尚父曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.4">“黃帝修三員，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.5">備日行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.6">習無智，【19】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.7">[...] 設皆紀， [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.8">四正受任，???</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-14a.9">五 事（?）皆[...] 【20】???</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.15 (STRIP 21) MACHENGYUAN 9: 216 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.1">[...] 問日行”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.2">尚父曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.3">“日行乎，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.4">用以果,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.5">而波（被/潛/憯）以成,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.6">鄰而均庶，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.7">遠而先達,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-15a.8">此日行也.”【21A】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.16 (STRIP 21B) MACHENGYUAN 9: 217 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.1">堯王天下，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.2">備[=服]方,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.3">恒吝長明，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-16a.4">行四 [...]【21B】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.17 (STRIP 22) MACHENGYUAN 9: 218 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.1">[...] 訪之於子，[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.2">曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.3">“從政何先?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.4">禹答曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.5">“唯志.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-17a.6">堯 [...]【22】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.18 (STRIP 23) MACHENGYUAN 9: 219 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-18a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.1">[...] 則物生，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.2">瀆則智成，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.3">金厚不流，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-18a.4">玉則不戡.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.19 (STRIP 23) MACHENGYUAN 9: 219 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-19a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.1">堯以四害之紊爲未也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.2">乃問於禹曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.3">“大害既制，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-19a.4">小[...]”【23】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.20 (STRIPS 24-25) MACHENGYUAN 9: 220-221 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.1">居時何先?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.2">曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.3">“毋忘其所不能.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.4">堯曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.5">“嗚呼！</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.6">日月閟間，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.7">歲盡（?) [...]”【24】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.8">察之於堯，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-20a.9">堯始用之嘉德 [...]【25】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.21 (STRIP 26) MACHENGYUAN 9: 222 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-21a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.1">舜王天下，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.2">三苗不賓，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.3">舜不割其道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-21a.4">不塞其 [...]【26】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.22 (STRIPS 27-28, 29A) MACHENGYUAN 9: 224-225 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.1">[...] 曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.2">理政固在長，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.3">請 [...]【27】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.4">[...] 失也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.5">怨并之眾人也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.6">非能合德於世者也，【28】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.7">[...] 明則保國，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.8">知賢政治，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-22a.9">教美民服. 【29A】</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.23 (STRIPS 29-30) MACHENGYUAN 9: 226-227 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.1">禹王天下，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.2">服深恒厚 [...]【29B】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.3">五年而天下正.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.4">一曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.5">禹事堯，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-23a.6">天下大水.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.24 (STRIP 30) MACHENGYUAN 9: 227 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-24a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.1">堯乃就禹曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.2">“乞汝其往，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.3">疏川啓谷，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-24a.4">以瀆天下.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.25 (STRIPS 30-31) MACHENGYUAN 9: 227-229 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.1">禹疏江爲三，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.2">疏河【30】爲九，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.3">百川皆導，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.4">塞敷九十，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.5">決瀆三百，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-25a.6">首耇黧 (=句指 'curved'), 身命[min= lin 鱗?]粗</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.26 (STRIPS 31-32) MACHENGYUAN 9: 229-231 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-26a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.1">禹使民以二和，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.2">民乃盡力.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.3">百川既【31】導，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-26a.4">天下能恒.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.27 (STRIPS 32-33) MACHENGYUAN 9: 231-233 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.1">二曰: Another said:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.2">"奉舜踵德</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.3">施于四國，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.4">誨以勞民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.5">畿而盡.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.6">禹奮中疾志，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.7">有欲而弗【32】違,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.8">深, 實, 固, 疏 [=湑]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-27a.9">有功而弗廢.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUZHIWANGTIANXIA 9.57.28 (STRIPS 33-34) MACHENGYUAN 9: 233-234 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.1">三曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.2">禹王天下，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.3">昭大志</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.4">不私 [...]【33】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.5">[...]棄身， [...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.6">生行勞民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.7">死行不祭，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.8">前行建功，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.9">中行固同，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0085_tls_001-28a.10">終行不[窮?] [...]【34】</seg>
                </p>

